# Phase 13 UAT evidence-custody directory (D-08).
#
# This directory is the canonical custody location for the GATE-02 empirical
# verification. Plan 13-02 writes all live-run captures here BEFORE Plan 13-03
# tears the ngx worktree down (worktree removal discards uncommitted artifacts;
# memory feedback_worktree_artifact_loss):
#
#   *.streamjson   -- raw `claude -p --output-format stream-json` captures (parent)
#   *.report.md    -- extracted parent .result (SHAPE grade source, SC-1/SC-2)
#   *.agent.md     -- extracted subagent JSONL text (BUDGET source, SC-4)
#   *.err          -- stderr per run (out_of_credits / 429 detection)
#   PASS-K.md      -- the Pass@k / Pass^k table per skill + overall
#   grade logs     -- per-run SHAPE + BUDGET verdicts
#
# It lives in the lz-advisor planning tree, NOT the throwaway worktree, so it
# survives `git worktree remove`. WORKTREE-PROVENANCE.md (this same directory)
# already records the SC-3 worktree provenance.
